isHistoryOlder

public int isHistoryOlder(OMVOntology o,
                          org.semanticweb.kaon2.api.Ontology registry1,
                          org.semanticweb.kaon2.api.Ontology registry2,
                          java.lang.String lsp,
                          java.util.List<OMVChange> changes2ori)
Compares if change history in registry is older than in registry2

Parameters:
o - is the ontology from which we want to compare change history
registry1 - is the registry that will be compared
registry2 - is the registry that will be used as reference
lsp - is the URI of the last synchronization point of the two logs
changes2ori - is the list of changes from the remote registry (the reference)
Returns:
int -1 = error 0 = false 1 = true 2 = unknown 3 = special 0 - lastChange1=lastChange2, but something earlier is missing from the remote log 4 = special 1 - lastChange1lastChange2, but something earlier is missing from the remote log
